data.description: Professional photos and details coming soon! Find peaceful living in the desirable, beautifully landscaped Arbor Meadows. This charming ranch home is situated on a corner lot across from the community's tree-lined park and gazebo. Step inside to find lofty ceilings, and an inviting open layout where the living room steals the spotlight with a welcoming gas fireplace. The thoughtfully designed kitchen is filled with natural light and equipped with stainless-steel appliances and gas range. There is a generous amount of pantry and closet space, and the main floor laundry room is tucked discreetly close by. On the west side of the home, you'll find professionally cleaned, low-profile carpet where two bedrooms share a full bathroom. At the end of the hallway, walk into the spacious primary bedroom with ensuite bathroom and a sliding door leading to the backyard. Build value by finishing the massive basement or take advantage of the generous storage space complete with mats, shelves, and the sound booth installed for recording. Lots of upgrades including Pulse Fiber, an active radon mitigation system, and furnace humidifier. Enjoy an easy walk to Old St. Louis Natural Area, Osborn Park, and Winona Outdoor Pool and the convenience of shopping, schools, eateries, and medical facilities just moments away.
